survey_response.review_text: My tooth filling had came out, which was done long back, visited 2 doctors before this both of them suggested for tooth canal as I was doubtful to go ahead was bearing with the pain from 2 months. After i visited this clinic doctor explained the situation and suggested tooth canal was not required just filled the tooth and fixed a crown.

Visited doc with a gum infection and a cavity, However i was anxious about the procedure in the beginning, but the service I recieved has beyond my expectations. Almost a pain-free root canal treatment and reassurance throughout the procedure. Thankyou so much doctor Naveen!

The services that I receive from Dr Naveen N is excellent. 
He explained everything to me in a very clear manner.
It’s rare to find a doctor that combines such personal touch and care for a patient. I highly recommend him to anyone looking for a specialist.

The doctor is good in his job. However unprofessional when it comes to keeping up the time. I had booked an appointment at 5:00 pm and was there in the clinic at 5:05 to 5:10. The security said he might come any moment. No sign of the doctor. When I re-entered the clinic at 5:30, there was another patient being catered to. I waited for 15 to 20 mins, but no slot yet. 
  As a professional courtesy, I was expecting the doctor to call and communicate his availability. If there was another patient at his doorstep, then I was expecting him to call me and let me know  when he is available.
